articles.author: Martin Pegan
articles.title: World Test Championship hero backs India pace attack to fire in Final - ICC Cricket
articles.description: India have the pace attack to trouble Australia in the World Test Championship Final in England even if Jasprit Bumrah remains sidelined through injury, according to WTC winner Ross Taylor.
